Description: JBoss Overlord Run Time Governance (RTGov) 1.0 for JBossAS allows remote authenticated users to execute arbitrary Java code via an MVFLEX Expression Language (MVEL) expression. NOTE: some of these details are obtained from third party information.

Name: CVE-2013-6491
Description: The python-qpid client (common/rpc/impl_qpid.py) in OpenStack Oslo before 2013.2 does not enforce SSL connections when qpid_protocol is set to ssl, which allows remote attackers to obtain sensitive information by sniffing the network.

Name: CVE-2013-6492
